b'Macross FB7: Ore no Uta wo Kike!': b'In 2059, five decades after the Space War I conflict seen in the first Macross story. Macross Frontier, the 25th New Macross Class super-long-distance colonization fleet, is journeying through the galaxy to a new paradise to call home. However, it is locked in a state of war with a strange enemy called Vajra.\n\nMacross FB7 is the 30th anniversary work of the Macross franchise.'
